  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The period of taking students to the first grade can be extended further",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Education Mr. Susil Premajayantha also said in the Parliament that there is a possibility to extend the period of admission of students to the first grade.",
        "The Minister of Education said this while answering a question asked by the chief organizer of the party Mr. Lakshman Kiriella.",
        "\"Is it possible to extend the enrollment period for children in the first grade? Many people have called me and asked this matter.\""
      ],
